#

Grilled Chicken with Avocado Salsa

35 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

GrilledHealthyQuick

Description

Juicy grilled chicken topped with a refreshing avocado salsa for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 2 large
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • tomato: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 medium
  • lime: 1
  • cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
